+# GitHub controlled-publication adapter — 0276-r3
+
+The adapter preserves plan, dry-run and apply separation and reuses the existing
+remote mutation gate. A stdlib `urllib` transport is available, but every apply
+requires an injected 0276-r4 collision-guard receipt. Therefore r3 cannot be
+used alone to mutate GitHub.
+
+The token is accepted only at the call boundary, sent in the Authorization
+header and excluded from every result. Tests use an injected fake transport.
