+# Changelog — 0276-r3 GitHub controlled-publication adapter
+
+## Added
+
+- added an injected REST transport protocol and stdlib implementation;
+- reused the default-closed remote mutation gate;
+- refused apply without an r4 guard receipt.
+
+## Boundaries
+
+- one existing Scheduler only;
+- SQL remains durable authority;
+- GitHub mutation remains closed unless this phase explicitly reaches the guarded adapter;
+- no secret is serialized.
